of 2006. we raised $53.40billion in net cash from
financing activities, primarily in
long-term borrowings as
well as through secured financings, partially offset by common
stock repurchases. we used net cash of $57.37billion in
our operating and investing activities, primarily to capitalize
on trading and investing opportunities for our clients and
ourselves.
